   VECTOR MACHINE; HOA BINH PROVINCE; 3 GORGES AREA; FREQUENCY RATIO;
   WENCHUAN EARTHQUAKE; SPATIAL PREDICTION},
Author-Email = {hr.pourghasemi@shirazu.ac.ir},
