   Demiray, Bekir Z., Univ Iowa, Dept Comp Sci, Iowa City, IA 52242 USA.
   Xiang, Zhongrun; Ewing, Gregory J.; Demir, Ibrahim, Univ Iowa, Dept Civil \& Environm Engn, Iowa City, IA 52242 USA.
