   Crop; Random forest regression (RFR)},
Keywords-Plus = {LEAF-AREA INDEX; NEURAL-NETWORK ESTIMATION; RADIATIVE-TRANSFER MODEL;
   CHLOROPHYLL CONTENT; REMOTE ESTIMATION; SPECTRAL REFLECTANCE; RANDOM
   FOREST; CANOPY VARIABLES; BAND SELECTION; GRASSLAND},
