   Xu, Xiangming, East Mailing Res, Genet \& Crop Improvement, NIAB EMR, W Mailing, England.
   Li, Qingdong; Guo, Lei, Beihang Univ, Sch Elect Engn \& Automat, Beijing 100191, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.compag.2018.10.017},
Keywords = {Wheat yellow rust; multispectral image; Spectral vegetation index (SVI);
