   Yang, Jun, Liaoning Normal Univ, Human Settlements Res Ctr, Dalian 110169, Peoples R China.
   Xiao, Xiangming, Univ Oklahoma, Ctr Spatial Anal, Dept Microbiol \& Plant Biol, Norman, OK 73019 USA.
   Xia, Jianhong (Cecilia), Curtin Univ, Sch Earth \& Planetary Sci EPS, Perth, WA 65630, Australia.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.buildenv.2022.109000},
