   Ge, Xiangyu; Wang, Jingzhe; Ding, Jianli; Cao, Xiaoyi; Zhang, Zipeng; Liu, Jie; Li, Xiaohang, Xinjiang Univ, Key Lab Oasis Ecol, Urumqi, Xinjiang, Peoples R China.},
