   Kattge, Jens; Reichstein, Markus, Max Planck Inst Biogeochem MPI BGC, Jena, Germany.
   Kramer, Koen, Wageningen Univ, Wageningen Environm Res WUR, Wageningen, Netherlands.
   Cornelissen, J. Hans C., Vrije Univ, Dept Ecol Sci, Syst Ecol, Amsterdam, Netherlands.
   Reich, Peter, Univ Minnesota, Dept Forest Resources, St Paul, MN 55108 USA.
