   Shukla, U. K., Banaras Hindu Univ, Ctr Adv Study Geol, Inst Sci, Varanasi 221005, Uttar Pradesh, India.
   Dieu Tien Bui, Duy Tan Univ, Inst Res \& Dev, Da Nang 550000, Vietnam.
   Mishra, Varun Narayan, Suresh Gyan Vihar Univ, Ctr Climate Change \& Water Res, Jaipur 302017, Rajasthan, India.
   Bhardwaj, Anshuman, Univ Aberdeen, Kings Coll, Sch Geosci, Meston Bldg, Aberdeen AB24 3UE, Scotland.
   Bhardwaj, Anshuman, Lulea Univ Technol, Dept Comp Sci Elect \& Space Engn, Div Space Technol, S-97187 Lulea, Sweden.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.scitotenv.2020.141565},
Article-Number = {141565},
Keywords = {Flood susceptibility mapping; ANFIS; Genetic algorithm (GA);
   Differential evolution (DE); Particle swarm optimization (PSO);
