   Wu, WB (Corresponding Author), Minist Agr, Key Lab Agr Remote Sensing, Beijing 100081, Peoples R China.
   Xiao, JF (Corresponding Author), Univ New Hampshire, Earth Syst Res Ctr, Inst Study Earth Oceans \& Space, Durham, NH 03824 USA.
