   Souza, Roberto; Rittner, Leticia; Lotufo, Roberto A., Univ Campinas UNICAMP, Sch Elect \& Comp Engn, BR-13083970 Campinas, SP, Brazil.
   Benediktsson, Jon Atli, Univ Iceland, Fac Elect \& Comp Engn, IS-107 Reykjavik, Iceland.},
