   Bangira, Tsitsi; Alfieri, Silvia Maria; Menenti, Massimo, Delft Univ Technol, Dept Geoscience \& Remote Sensing, POB 5048, NL-2600 GA Delft, Netherlands.
   Menenti, Massimo, Chinese Acad Sci, State Key Lab Remote Sensing Sci, Inst Remote Sensing \& Digital Earth, Beijing 100101, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.3390/rs11111351},
