   Benediktsson, Jon Atli; Chanussot, Jocelyn, Univ Iceland, Fac Elect \& Comp Engn, IS-101 Reykjavik, Iceland.
   Du, Peijun, Nanjing Univ, Key Lab Satellite Mapping Technol \& Applicat, State Adm Surveying Mapping \& Geoinformat China, Nanjing 210093, Jiangsu, Peoples R China.
   Chanussot, Jocelyn, Grenoble Inst Technol, GIPSA Lab, F-38400 Grenoble, France.},
DOI = {10.1109/JSTARS.2016.2636877},
