   Gong, Peng; Wang, Lin, Chinese Acad Sci, Inst Remote Sensing Applicat, State Key Lab Remote Sensing Sci, Beijing 100101, Peoples R China.
   Gong, Peng; Wang, Lin, Beijing Normal Univ, Beijing 100101, Peoples R China.
