   sensing; geographical information system (GIS); Rudraprayag district;
   Indian Himalayan Region (IHR)},
Keywords-Plus = {KERNEL LOGISTIC-REGRESSION; ROCK SLOPE STABILITY; LAND-USE CHANGE;
