   Abdullah-Al-Faisal, Medecins Sans Frontieres MSF, GIS Unit, Operat Ctr Amsterdam OCA, Coxs Bazar 4750, Bangladesh.
   Naim, Md Nazmul Huda; Sikdar, Md Soumik, Chittagong Univ Engn \& Technol CUET, Dept Urban \& Reg Planning, Chattogram 4349, Bangladesh.
   Naim, Md Nazmul Huda; Sikdar, Md Soumik, Bangladesh Rural Adv Comm BRAC, Coxs Bazar, Bangladesh.
   Kona, Marium Akter, Bangladesh Army Univ Engn \& Technol, Dept Civil Engn, Natore 6431, Bangladesh.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.rsase.2020.100463},
EarlyAccessDate = {JAN 2021},
