   Goncalves, Wesley Nunes; Marcato Junior, Jose, Univ Fed Mato Grosso do Sul, Fac Engn Architecture \& Urbanism \& Geog, Campo Grande, MS, Brazil.
   Li, Jonathan, Univ Waterloo, Dept Geog \& Environm Management, Waterloo, ON N2L 3G1, Canada.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.isprsjprs.2020.05.022},
Keywords = {Multi-spectral LiDAR; CNN; Land-cover classification; Hyper-parameters},
