   Huang, Wei, Beijing Normal Univ, Fac Geog Sci, State Key Lab Remote Sensing Sci, Beijing, Peoples R China.
   Sun, Lin, Shandong Univ Sci \& Technol, Coll Geodesy \& Geomat, Qingdao, Peoples R China.
   Zhu, Xiaolin, Hong Kong Polytech Univ, Dept Land Surveying \& Geoinformat, Hong Kong, Peoples R China.
   Yuan, Qiangqiang, Wuhan Univ, Sch Geodesy \& Geomat, Wuhan, Peoples R China.
   Liu, Lei, Lanzhou Univ, Coll Earth \& Environm Sci, Lanzhou, Peoples R China.},
DOI = {10.1016/j.rse.2020.112005},
